委員會開綠燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋係時候開始討論當中嘅細節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n試過有法官判示威者以胸部襲警後，相信大家都明白香港有好多紅底法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以獨立調查委員會一定唔可以只係有本地法官組成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要嘅獨立調查委員會係<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>由國際專家、聯合國，甚至海牙軍事法庭嘅人組成</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>拒絕港共自己人查自己人<br />\n<br />\n要由國際專家調查事件</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2ca44f755a7acb40b0110d218f93b82eff7d02","tid":1395281,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T00:27:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac9d986854e8f9b63058b1a47f0415799ff52413","tid":1395281,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T00:27:44.000Z","msg":"［廣傳］ 有咩人組成獨立調查委員會？！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1389165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1389165</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7fdf1ce3357151d7b7a2f392dacc79fc791ea4ad","tid":1395281,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T00:42:40.000Z","msg":"咪再北上啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚恐怖"},{"pid":"2eb1a7e903b2aa8a57b1ff688ea3281a286dcb6b","tid":1395281,"uid